#MOBILES
#11001
plains skeleton~
a plains skeleton~
A plains skeleton walks here, apparently unaware of it's surroundings.
~
It walks the plains in an almost undead form, the plains skeleton has been
derived by the body of a dead person, who unlike the undead is made up of no
remaining flesh or other means of identifying it's previous life, and has not
the simple decency of having died and put to rest.  Instead it roams the land
in a state of consciousness unrecognizing of anything around it, obviuosly
driven by some higher, aweful source.
~
