#ROOMS
#11001
The Western Plains~
A large plain opens to your west. You have entered The Western Plains. This 
great land is known for it's great production of cotton and many mysterious
and obvious dangers. For a second, you are stopped by the massive waves of
wind that almost knock you off your feet and send chills up your spine. 
The land is grassy and there is nothing special that you can make out by 
looking west, except for endless grass.
The north and south seem to be blocked by piles of rock.
~
