#11019
Defile in the Short Mountains~
You are walking in somewhere strange.  It is a narrow underground path within
the mountains.  It is relatively dark with little light coming in through the
crack in the rocks, and a cold wind blows constantly from it, making this place
almost unbarable.  More of it seems to be coming from the west end of the
defile, and you could go there or go back into the fields through the crack to
the east, if you can fig up the place you came out of.  It seems to be covered
with rocks and dirt, so may take some digging.
~
