The West Gate~
You stand in a mean looking wooden gate, about 15-20 feet high. Nothing
special about it. It seems to be built into the town's stone wall.  The gate
is made of some of the strongest wood around and you can see scratches and 
dents that it has suffered in the past while keeping the enemy from just 
walking in. To the west you see endless grassy plains.
You can see huge piles of rocks blocking your way north and south.
~
